_header: Light into the world now doth spring and shine
Subjects: chronicles, verse in; Schism, papal; popes
_description: On the resignation of Pope Felix in favour of Pope Nicholas V, translating a Latin line which precedes it, in Part VII of Fabyan’s Chronicle, Septima Pars, Henrici Sexti — one couplet

HarEng766.Transcription:
Light into the world now doth spryng & shyneffor ffelix vnto
                    Nichas alle frely doth resyne
